            <title>Efficient Wind Energy Plants Through Condition Monitoring</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	A wind power plant&amp;#39;s reliability will determine its profitability. Any downtime will result in a financial loss. This 8-minute, 4-second video shows how condition monitoring systems can be used to identify failure risks and provide early warning for necessary maintenance or repair work. See how data from more than 1,000 wind turbines is collected and evaluated so the cost of maintenance or downtime can be better planned.&lt;/p&gt;
