	SKF is a leading global supplier in the areas of bearings, seals, mechatronics, services and lubrication systems. The group&amp;rsquo;s service offer includes technical support, maintenance services, engineering consultancy and training. SKF is represented in more than 130 countries and has 15,000 distributor locations worldwide. The group&amp;rsquo;s annual sales 2009 were SEK 56,227 million. The number of employees was 41,172.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/condition_monitoring/~4/h164pH7ARyk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
