            <title>Infrared thermography and condition monitoring at the zoo</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Think your workplace is a zoo? Try using predictive maintenance technologies in a real zoo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/condition_monitoring/~4/7spXuon2ENw" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
