            <title>Performing infrared thermography on motors</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	TEGG Services talks about using infrared thermography to perform predictive maintenance on motors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/condition_monitoring/~4/QqhAiidJ7FE" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-07-15T15:48:53-05:00</a10:updated>
